    "This property will be used in Section 6.1.",
    "The fact that the pre-training of transformer models can be performed in an unsupervised fashion on a large text corpus is very important.",
    "It enables transfer learning, i.e.",
    "transferring the language-understanding skill acquired during pre-training to an applied task with a much smaller data volume.",
    "As will be shown in Section 7.1, the transformer model can be fine-tuned on the application-specific text corpus if required, at significantly reduced effort."
